#: ../../language/error_codes/E0055.md:7
msgid ""
"The FFI parameter of pointer type should be annotated with either "
"`#borrow` or\\ `#owned`, the default calling convention is currently "
"`#owned` and it will be\\ changed in the future. For the detailed "
"meaning, checkout [FFI documentation](/language/ffi.md#the-borrow-and-"
"owned-attribute)."
